```bash
./health.sh
```

Save the report:

```bash
./health.sh > health_report.txt
```

Append future reports:

```bash
./health.sh >> health_history.log
```

Save errors separately:

```bash
./health.sh > health_report.txt 2> health_error.log
```

Save everything:

```bash
./health.sh &> complete_report.log
```

